WEBVTT

00:11.000 --> 00:14.500
Right now, I'm here at IVT Institute Islamabad...

00:15.500 --> 00:19.000
and Sir Ali's student, Sufiyan...

00:19.000 --> 00:21.500
has done my haircut.

00:21.500 --> 00:24.000
He has given me a complete fade with a full hair cut...

00:24.000 --> 00:26.000
And Mashallah, looking awesome..

00:26.000 --> 00:28.500
If you look closely...

00:28.500 --> 00:32.000
you can clearly see the sharpness and cleanliness.

00:32.000 --> 00:35.500
the level of perfection in his hands...

00:35.500 --> 00:41.400
it's a professional job that he done, not many people can achieve this kind of perfection.

00:41.400 --> 00:43.000
And if I say this,

00:43.000 --> 00:48.500
Sufyan's work is just like my Berber, with whom I do the cutting myself,
00:48.500 --> 00:50.500
he will not have that much perfection in his hand.

00:50.500 --> 00:52.000
"To be Honest!"

00:52.000 --> 00:52.800
So... 

00:52.800 --> 00:54.000
A big thank you to Sir Ali...

00:54.000 --> 00:55.500
and especially to Sufiyan

00:55.500 --> 00:58.500
who done this amazing cutting.

00:58.500 --> 01:00.000
Thank you!